maml:Description.maml:para: The TeamProjectCollection URL. Ex.: https://tfs2015.local/tfs/defaultcollection. Note: if the 'Tfs' parameter was informed, this parameter will be ignored.
The name of the Team Project the Area belongs.
Area path without the Team Project (Ex.: \Area 1\Sub-area 3).
Users and/or groups to grant permissions.
Actions to be granted: WORK_ITEM_READ, WORK_ITEM_WRITE, GENERIC_READ, GENERIC_WRITE, CREATE_CHILDREN, DELETE, MANAGE_TEST_PLANS
The area URI. Got from New-Area. Ex.: vstfs:///Classification/Node/71e08ab3-62f7-4a9a-8430-fdcfca626401.
An instance of the object TfsTeamProjectCollection, that represents a TeamProjectCollection. If informed the CollectionUrl will be ignored.
If informed, will deny the the action for the user and/or group informed.
